{"tid":363787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社：律政司高層建議不上訴，但袁國強堅持申請覆核黃之鋒等人刑期","createTime":"2017-08-18T01:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T02:51:34.000Z","uid":91152,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"122551ab8f5939599deebe087e5de7dd03d7122f","tid":363787,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:13:22.000Z","msg":"A senior government source who declined to be identified due to the sensitivity of the matter said Hong Kong's top prosecutors had initially &quot;not recommended pursuing&quot; the case further after the non-jail terms were handed down.<br />\n<br />\nBut Hong Kong's Secretary of Justice, Rimsky Yuen, overruled them and insisted on re-opening Wong's case, a decision that ultimately led to their imprisonment, the source said.<br />\n<br />\nIn response to emailed questions from Reuters to Yuen seeking clarification, a spokesman for the Department of Justice said it &quot;does not comment on internal discussions regarding individual cases&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;However, the DoJ (Department of Justice) reiterates that all decisions were made in accordance with the Prosecution Code, the applicable law and relevant evidence.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe DoJ said in an earlier statement there was &quot;absolutely no basis to imply any political motive&quot;."},{"pid":"0cf5eca75d484e5cc3e5d5a8f2bb6209b53fb463","tid":363787,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死共狗收左幾錢呀"},{"pid":"bdaba62b17ee18f61dbdf7e9e8e8a84e28698999","tid":363787,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:18:16.000Z","msg":"毒果<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】雙學三子衝入公民廣場一案，律政司在原審裁判官判決半年後，上訴覆核刑期。路透社昨引述政府高層消息指，港府高層檢控人員（top prosecutors）在原審裁決各人毋須監禁後，最初是不建議上訴（not recommended pursuing），但律政司長袁國強出手推翻建議，堅持上訴重開案件（Rimsky Yuen, overruled them and insisted on re-opening Wong's case)。<br />\n<br />\n人權組織轟政治心虛<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述消息人士指，袁國強的決定最終導致三子入獄，律政司回覆路透社時未有直接否認消息，僅稱「不評論有關個別案件的內部討論」，又重申所有決定均有依照檢控守則、有關法律及相關證據。<br />\n律政司昨晚發表聲明，聲稱香港司法獨立的情況「不可能被質疑」。對於有人指案件的檢控有政治目的甚至政治迫害，律政司表示指控「全無基礎，更漠視本案客觀存在的證據」，又稱判案書的理據顯示法院純以法律角度處理本案，「不可能存在任何政治動機」。<br />\n律政司表示，本案3名被告並非因為行使公民自由權利而被定罪，而是因為他們抗議時的行為觸犯法律。律政司指上訴法庭的判案書釐清相關法律原則和量刑準則，能為日後同類案件提供指引。<br />\n國際組織人權觀察中國部主任Sophie Richarson則批評，律政司以牽強理由提出刑期覆核，並非考量公共秩序，而是心虛的政治動作，目的是阻止這3人參選立法會，同時嚇阻未來抗議活動。"},{"pid":"e0edd88e44e150cb21fe3cd0d5765469a7348d1d","tid":363787,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:18:53.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong's Secretary of Justice, Rimsky Yuen, overruled them and insisted on re-opening Wong's case, a decision that ultimately led to their imprisonment<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661b837760d4d91e89f78acfc03e1f2d0db10a99","tid":363787,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:19:25.000Z","msg":"又推個人出嚟受標耙"},{"pid":"fa2468d4669b1ce1ca4b10dee367de8d8e0d0618","tid":363787,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:20:04.000Z","msg":"下屆特首：袁國強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb20f9ebace4b6d3563b29f100638c36b8509fd","tid":363787,"uid":25298,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:23:50.000Z","msg":"強國猿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e313c2537e451ab674e0a7e6c5dd875c61386d","tid":363787,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"又一男子因素"},{"pid":"4ace5f62581e695d843314b3e6e83f6ac052d80b","tid":363787,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:27:18.000Z","msg":"香港制度係兩邊都可以就刑期上訴<br />\n咁佢三個都會再上訴至終審，都唔知扮灰做咩"},{"pid":"873c429a3f5d8610c7f2a23d7e6ba124a446f4d9","tid":363787,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:28:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E6%A1%88-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%BC%95%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%BC%B7%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0-%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&d=sG%2F3FYmKfJ8rriiEDeMithFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=33ed1362\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%258C%2581%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%2F&h=980b49ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E6%A1%88-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%BC%95%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%BC%B7%E6%8E%A8%E7%BF%BB%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0-%E5%A0%85%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4/</a><br />\n<br />\n「雙學三子」羅冠聰、黃之鋒、周永康因926公民廣場案，今日被改判囚6至8個月，引發國際社會關注。《路透社》引述政府高層消息稱，高層檢控人員原本不建議就刑期覆核，但律政司長袁國強堅持上訴，終令三子入獄。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">《路透社》今日引述一位不願具名的政府高層消息稱，案件早前判三人不用監禁，當時律政司內的高層檢控人員不建議政府上訴。不過袁國強卻推翻檢控人員的建議，堅持重開雙學三子的案件。</span><br />\n<br />\n報道引述律政司方面回應，稱不會就個別案件的內部討論作回應，但重申所有決定均是依照《檢控守則》、有關法律及相關證據作出。<br />\n<br />\n另外律政司在晚上9時許發聲明，指外界的政治迫害等指控全無基礎，本港司法獨立「不可能被質疑」。聲明指，從判案書可見法院是用法律角度處理本案，不可能存在任何政治動機。"},{"pid":"700d6b5f2f68de24164e97e48d65f81cc0410280","tid":363787,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港制度係兩邊都可以就刑期上訴<br />\n咁佢三個都會再上訴至終審，都唔知扮灰做咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要即時監禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fce08d1a6639c3b4f7c7490e1eb98ee775098f9","tid":363787,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:50:08.000Z","msg":"仲話大和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea13f320bd8ae36eac9a0b947d53efd0d5badcc","tid":363787,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:51:23.000Z","msg":"市民可唔可以就七警案期上訴<br />\n知法犯法唔係罪加一等咩 ?"},{"pid":"a963e69ff17c6e31c1291dc7e090dbf79d4f6ac9","tid":363787,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T01:52:29.000Z","msg":"懷疑強國袁同飯民打籠通 佢想啟動佔中迫爆監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cccc042f6c4f1c0d5612d4659a61806e9d2805","tid":363787,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T02:15:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>市民可唔可以就七警案期上訴<br />\n知法犯法唔係罪加一等咩 ?</blockquote><br />\n問下袁國強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab8d2951a948ff333b96a8e725139a5c70f0863","tid":363787,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T09:26:35.000Z